root: ^Looks like you can't catch a break, Zip.
^Despite the debris and black hole, someone else decided to move into the area. The questionnaire she filled out says she's a doctor looking to use TAPS plants for medical research.
^Also says she's admittedly not as patient as other customers so she'll be wanting her deliveries quicker. However, she notes she's very rewarding when those demands are met.
^Well, whatever. I'm sure you'll be fine. You've been doing well so far.
